193
00:06:39,390 --> 00:06:41,560
<font face="MS Gothic" size="20"><b>若造も食べろ</b></font>


195
00:06:41,560 --> 00:06:42,610
<font face="MS Gothic" size="20"><b>あぁ</b></font>


197
00:06:43,520 --> 00:06:44,940
<font face="MS Gothic" size="20"><b>ありがとう 爺さん</b></font>


199
00:06:53,280 --> 00:06:54,280
<font face="MS Gothic" size="20"><b>誰なの</b></font>


201
00:06:54,830 --> 00:06:57,620
<font face="MS Gothic" size="20"><b>宮廷魔法使いのデンケン様です</b></font>


203
00:06:58,830 --> 00:07:00,920
<font face="MS Gothic" size="20"><b>宮廷魔法使い…</b></font>


205
00:07:05,460 --> 00:07:07,550
<font face="MS Gothic" size="20"><b>お貴族様じゃねえか!</b></font>


207
00:07:07,840 --> 00:07:11,090
<font face="MS Gothic" size="20"><b>あの タメ口たたいてすみませんでした</b></font>


209
00:07:11,720 --> 00:07:13,050
<font face="MS Gothic" size="20"><b>構わん</b></font>


211
00:07:13,050 --> 00:07:16,350
