215
00:07:20,980 --> 00:07:23,770
<font face="MS Gothic" size="20"><b>どうせ金の使い道などない</b></font>


217
00:07:23,770 --> 00:07:26,020
<font face="MS Gothic" size="20"><b>ないってことはないでしょ</b></font>


219
00:07:26,520 --> 00:07:28,780
<font face="MS Gothic" size="20"><b>そうです お孫さんとか…</b></font>


221
00:07:30,650 --> 00:07:33,740
<font face="MS Gothic" size="20"><b>儂には子も孫もおらん</b></font>


223
00:07:33,740 --> 00:07:37,490
<font face="MS Gothic" size="20"><b>儂が２０半ばの時に妻に先立たれた</b></font>


225
00:07:39,540 --> 00:07:42,120
<font face="MS Gothic" size="20"><b>元々体が弱かった</b></font>


227
00:07:43,250 --> 00:07:45,000
<font face="MS Gothic" size="20"><b>政争に敗れた</b></font>


229
00:07:45,000 --> 00:07:48,300
